{"id": 1457, "genre": 1001, "title": "你的与众不同都体现在什么小事上了？", "description": "动画角色的人设都要靠一些莫名其妙的小习惯才显得更有辨识度，所以你有什么“很你”的小习惯吗？（题图来自：Léonard Dupond）", "record_count": 12074, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170118120704JsQ3IfbOYNjln87E.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-06T03:00:06Z", "options": [{"id": 162560, "content": "不要各种椒，青椒，红椒，灯笼椒", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926632}, {"id": 162816, "content": "为了不同而不同~???", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898026}, {"id": 163584, "content": "不能坐我宿舍的床", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 309373}, {"id": 165632, "content": "行为准则分人分事分物", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933650}, {"id": 175104, "content": "一年四季都要盖被子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952379}, {"id": 162561, "content": "冬天必须戴眼罩穿毛巾袜套上长长的加绒加厚睡袍睡觉?‍♂️否则睡不着?", "image": "img/option/option/20170206131821HV50Ytfj9IDc7an8.jpg", "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924185}, {"id": 162817, "content": "没吃过的 没干过的都想来一次 这或许勇于挑战也是我的一种不同吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 709226}, {"id": 163073, "content": "相比身边人，好像活百度", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429100}, {"id": 164353, "content": "不用标点\n讨厌叹号", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930650}, {"id": 164865, "content": "说话时刻保持微笑，笑点低，且爱大笑。时刻把变形金刚、擎天柱挂在嘴边。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931381}, {"id": 162562, "content": "对很大众的事物第一反应是抵触", "image": "img/option/option/20170206132551tANVn049ilSayKUX.jpg", "praise_count": 354, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906643}, {"id": 162818, "content": "碰见微博的网喷就想路见不平拔刀相助", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926982}, {"id": 163074, "content": "看到狗会上去搭话", "image": "img/option/option/20170206235656CaLEDqjGf4mJi13c.jpg", "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924516}, {"id": 165378, "content": "体重格外不同", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932898}, {"id": 162563, "content": "句子末喜欢加“~”", "image": null, "praise_count": 125, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 888130}, {"id": 162819, "content": "左手刷右边的牙齿，右手刷左边的牙齿，我不理解人有两只手为什么只用一只？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 103310}, {"id": 163075, "content": "有些菜只能用来下酒或者就着饮料喝绝不能用来下饭，比如大闸蟹", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927363}, {"id": 163843, "content": "孤独", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929643}, {"id": 164867, "content": "爱狗爱到把自己当成狗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931381}, {"id": 166659, "content": "手机App绝不归类，一归类就找不到。", "image": "img/option/option/20170214231753o421qLFrkU9hEvVx.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936721}, {"id": 172547, "content": "不爱吃煮饺，爱吃蒸饺，蒸饺配粥才好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952757}, {"id": 174595, "content": "从来没有要减肥的想法  (并没有我说我是瘦的人)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957757}, {"id": 162820, "content": "吃饺子不吃馅儿", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 901596}, {"id": 164100, "content": "特别喜欢吃食堂，喝那种刷锅水。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 779220}, {"id": 164612, "content": "不抽烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931158}, {"id": 165892, "content": "莫名其妙的冷漠", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 934359}, {"id": 166660, "content": "手机App绝对不能归类，一归类就找不到…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 936721}, {"id": 168452, "content": "喜欢写韩剧剧评", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061245}, {"id": 162565, "content": "火车上看不了文字，一看就晕，从小时候的绿皮车到如今的高铁", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 905876}, {"id": 162821, "content": "挤牙膏必须从后往前挤", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820186}, {"id": 163077, "content": "yy能力级强，各种yy，有时甚至可以一天……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902314}, {"id": 164613, "content": "3d眩晕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931158}, {"id": 162566, "content": "不玩王者不玩LOL不玩阴阳师不玩cscf不玩贴吧不玩微博", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 906938}, {"id": 163590, "content": "女孩子都喜欢拉帮结派去做的事情，我都喜欢一个人去……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916067}, {"id": 167174, "content": "喜独，自己一个人行动的时候状态非常自在，从小到大从来没被人欺负过，被评价为潇洒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937694}, {"id": 168710, "content": "一年半了都是手洗衣服，不用公共洗衣机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940869}, {"id": 162567, "content": "不出门不洗脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926648}, {"id": 162823, "content": "吹牛", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 911009}, {"id": 168711, "content": "不用梳子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940869}, {"id": 352520, "content": "我想让我喜欢的男生或女生用刀捅死我（我是男生，喜欢过男生也喜欢过女生）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688100}, {"id": 162568, "content": "握筷子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 849634}, {"id": 169224, "content": "感觉自己完美啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942131}, {"id": 162569, "content": "炒白菜必须放料酒算不算……", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 580048}, {"id": 162825, "content": "喜欢在各种社交软件和陌生人聊学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792424}, {"id": 163337, "content": "不急，慢慢来", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922196}, {"id": 162826, "content": "不说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 433392}, {"id": 163338, "content": "吃完饭必须站至少半小时后才坐下", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928061}, {"id": 162571, "content": "能看懂一些笑话", "image": "img/option/option/20170206133339VuOHaCzjWFT79DwJ", "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922126}, {"id": 162827, "content": "戒烟成功", "image": "img/option/option/20170206181956MvRQXzuayel3tdfn.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926998}, {"id": 163339, "content": "发完语音听一遍，或者两遍，甚至三遍。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 891793}]}